title: Babaeng nagnakaw ng sanggol, huli sa CCTV! | Reporter's Notebook
description: Aired (June 12, 2022): Nakunan ng CCTV camera ang ginawang pagtangay ng isang babae sa sanggol na anak ng mag-asawang sina Monique at Rodel. Sa kabutihang palad, nakita ang babae at napasakamay naman ng kinauukulan ang sanggol. Pero bago ito muling makasama nina Monique at Rodel, kailangan pa raw nila ng ebidensyang magpapatunay na sila ang mga magulang. title: Is Ukraine losing the artillery war in Donbas? | Ukraine latest
description: Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy said defending the Donbas region in eastern Ukraine was "vital" as the outcome would indicate "who will dominate in the coming weeks" of the war. "Hanging in there in Donbas is crucial," Zelenskyy said on Telegram in his daily address to the Ukrainian people. Russian forces have made recent advances in the Donbas and control most of the Luhansk region, with fighting especially intense in the city of Severodonetsk. Britain's Ministry of Defense said Wednesday on Twitter that Russian forces were now in control of the city of Sievierodonetsk. Elements of Ukraine's Armed Forces and several hundred civilians are sheltering in underground bunkers in Azot Chemical Plant in the city, the report added. Russia told Ukrainian forces holed up in the chemical plant to lay down their arms by early Wednesday.|Russia told Ukrainian forces deployed at a chemical plant in Sievierodonetsk to "stop their senseless resistance and lay down arms" from 8 a.m. Moscow time (0500 GMT)," on Wednesday, Mikhail Mizintsev, head of Russia's National Defense Management Center told the Interfax news agency. Civilians would be allowed to leave through a humanitarian corridor, he added. Ukraine says more than 500 civilians are currently trapped alongside soldiers inside the Azot chemical factory where its forces have defied weeks of Russian bombardment and assaults that have reduced much of the embattled city of Sievierodonetsk to ruins.|The West needs to send Ukraine "more heavy weapons" as it battles Russia's "brutal invasion," NATO Secretary General Jens Stoltenberg said. |NATO was already "stepping up" deliveries and officials would be meeting in Brussels on Wednesday to coordinate further support, Stoltenberg said at a news conference. On Tuesday, Ukraine's Defense Ministry said the country had only received a fraction of the arms it had requested and Polish Prime Minister Mateusz Morawiecki said the West was "not doing enough" to support Kyiv. Meanwhile, seven NATO nations pledged their support for Sweden and Finland's bids to join the military alliance. The support was voiced after a gathering at Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte's official residence in The Hague, co-hosted by his Danish counterpart, Mette Frederiksen. The other leaders in attendance were Romania's president and the prime ministers of Belgium, Poland, Portugal and Latvia.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #Donbas

title: Jokowi Resmi Reshuffle Kabinet: Hadi Tjahjanto jadi Menteri ATR, Zulkifli Hasan Duduki Posisi Mendag
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Joko Widodo akhirnya resmi melakukan reshuffle kabinet atau perombakan jajaran menterinya hari ini.||||Pelantikan Menteri dan Wakil Menteri Kabinet Indonesia Maju sisa masa jabatan Periode Tahun 2022-2024 dilakukan pukul 13.30 WIB di Istana negara.||||Harian KOMPAS, Rabu (15/06) memberitakan bahwa pelantikan akan diawali dengan kedatangan para pemimpin partai politik untuk bertemu dengan Presiden.||||Selanjutnya Presiden akan mengenalkan para menteri baru dan menteri yang bertukar posisi serta wakil menteri baru.  ||||Hari ini (15/06) Presiden Jokowi resmi melantik menterinya antara lain Hadi Tjahjanto duduki kursi Menteri ATR/BPN, Menteri Perdagangan resmi digantikan oleh Zulkifli Hasan yang juga Ketum PAN, serta Wakil Menteri Dalam Negeri diisi oleh John Wempi Wetimpo, Wakil Menteri Ketenagakerjaan diisi oleh Afriansyah Noor dan Politikus PSI Raja Juli Antoni resmi jadi Wamen ATR/BPN.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/299307/jokowi-resmi-reshuffle-kabinet-hadi-tjahjanto-jadi-menteri-atr-zulkifli-hasan-duduki-posisi-mendag
tags: breaking news|hadi tjahjanto|jokowi|kabinet indonesia maju|menteri atr|menteri perdagangan|pelantikan menteri|reshuffle kabinet|wakil menteri|zulkifli hasan

title: Rudy Giuliani Fires Back At January 6th Hearings
description: With our executive producer Rob out today, his assistant Winnie is sitting in the producer's chair, which means everyone is getting raises! Four states went to the polls today, Rudy Giuliani insists he wasn't drunk on election night, and a species of earthworms on steroids is invading the northeast.  And after James shows a photo of a man who had sneakers tattooed on his feet, Reggie explains why he'll never get a tattoo. title: U.S. Air Force clean chits C-17 cargo crew after Afghans plunged to death as Taliban took over
description: The crew of a US military cargo plane that civilians desperately hung onto during the chaotic withdrawal of American forces from Afghanistan has been cleared of wrongdoing. Several Afghan citizens had plunged to their death while clinging onto one of the last American planes and body parts were later found on the wheel well of the aircraft. The review team of US Air Force, however, has termed the aircrew's action appropriate. They also said the crew used sound judgment "in their decision to get airborne as quickly as possible when faced with an unprecedented and rapidly deteriorating security situation." The harrowing incident happened on August 16, 2021 a day after Taliban takeover. Watch this report to know more.|#afghanistan #cargoplane #usairforce #usanewstoday #usaircraft #afghanistannews #kabul #kabulairport #topgun #joebiden #taliban #washington

title: 104 hours with a snake & frog; How brave Chhattisgarh boy was rescued from 80-feet borewell
description: 11-year-old Rahul Sahu, who lived a nightmare for 104 hours, was rescued from an 80-feet deep borewell last night in Chhattisgarh. Around 500 personnel including army, NDRF and local police were a part of the operation since Rahul fell into the borewell on Friday while playing in the backyard of his residence in Pihrid village of Malkharoda development block. Officials say that he was stuck in the borewell with a snake and a frog. Chhattisgarh CM Bhupesh Baghel hailed the bravery of the boy and was in constant touch via video calls with the rescue team. A pipeline was installed for oxygen supply while Rahul was stuck inside. A 70-feet pit parallel to the borewell was dug up on Friday evening, while a 15-feet tunnel was constructed to connect the pit with the borewell. Watch this video for more details.|#chhattisgarh  #borewell  #borewellrescue  #bhupeshbaghel  #ndrf  #ndrfteam #army #chattisgarhnews

title: West Asia QUAD: India, Israel, US, UAE pact to take big leap during Bidenâ€™s Tel Aviv visit I Details
description: The first meeting of the India, Israel, US and UAE leaders' summit will take place next month during Joe Biden's in person visit to Tel Aviv. The US President will be in West Asia from July 13th to July 16th with stops in Israel, the West Bank, and Saudi Arabia. The new grouping of the 4 countries is known as I2U2 with I standing for India, Israel and U for US, UAE. The grouping is sometime referred to as the West Asian Quad. So far, the I2U2 has met only at foreign minister's level; the first meet was in October last year. Watch this report to know more about West Asia Quad.|#westasiaquad #quadmeeting #india #israel #usa #unitedstates #uae #joebiden #i2u2 #summit #tradetalks #foodsecurity #foodcrisis #uspresidentjoebiden

title: Klarifikasi Unggahan Candi Borobudur Mirip Jokowi, Roy Suryo: Itu Unggahan Dari Akun Twitter Lain!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Mantan Menpora, Roy Suryo mengklarifikasi foto editan patung Candi Borobudur mirip Presiden Joko Widodo.||||Sebelumnya, muncul unggahan foto patung Candi Borobudur diedit mirip Presiden Jokowi.||||Di akun twitternya, Roy Suryo menyebut unggahan itu dilakukan akun twitter lain.||||Roy mengaku menyimpan nama pengunggah pertamanya.||||Baca Juga Satgas Damai Cartenz Tangkap Dua Anggota KST Di Intan Jaya di https://www.kompas.tv/article/299168/satgas-damai-cartenz-tangkap-dua-anggota-kst-di-intan-jaya||||Agar tidak berkepanjangan, Roy menurunkan unggahan foto candi ini dari akun twitternya.||||Dikutip dari twitter @krmtroysuryo2 ditulis, "agar tidak ada yang memprovokasi lagi dan dianggap 'mengedit' karena ketidakfahamannya, maka postingan tersebut saya drop, case close."||||Lewat pesan Whatsapp kepada Kompas tv, Roy Suryo mengatakan, "justru itu saya sengaja menampilkan unggahan-unggahan yang sudah ada sebelumnya, makanya saya posting lengkap dengan nama pemosting pertamanya, bukan hanya memenya, jelas kan?."||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/299172/klarifikasi-unggahan-candi-borobudur-mirip-jokowi-roy-suryo-itu-unggahan-dari-akun-twitter-lain

title: J&K: Hindu banker's murder avenged; Forces kill Lashkar terrorist in Shopian encounter
description: Terrorists who killed Hindu banker Vijay Kumar in Kulgam have been gunned down in an encounter in J&K's Shopian. Total two terrorists were killed by the security forces in the Kanjiular area of Shopian. The slain Lashkar terrorists have been identified as Jan Mohammad Lone and Tufail Gunai. Jan Mohammad Lone who hails from Shopian had killed the bank manager on June 2 amid spate of targeted killings in Kashmir valley. Watch this report to know more.|#targetedkillings #jammuandkashmir #terrorist #hindu #shopianencounter #shopian #kulgam  #lashkar #encounter #terrorism #let

title: Politikus PSI Raja Juli Antoni Tiba di Istana Negara, Bakal jadi Wakil Menteri?
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Joko Widodo dikabarkan akan melakukan reshuffle kabinet atau perombakan jajaran menterinya hari ini.||||Berdasarkan informasi yang diterima Kompas TV, Pelantikan Menteri dan Wakil Menteri Kabinet Indonesia Maju sisa masa jabatan Periode Tahun 2022-2024 akan dilakukan pukul 13.30 WIB di Istana negara.||||Harian KOMPAS, Rabu (15/06)  memberitakan bahwa pelantikan akan diawali dengan kedatangan para pemimpin partai politik untuk bertemu dengan Presiden.||||Selanjutnya Presiden akan mengenalkan para menteri baru dan menteri yang bertukar posisi serta wakil menteri baru.  ||||Sebelumnya kemarin (14/06), Presiden Jokowi memang memanggil sejumlah menterinya antara lain Menteri Pertanian Syahrul Yasin Limpo, Menteri ATR/BPN Sofyan Djalil, Menteri Perdagangan Muhammad Lutfi, Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto, Wakil Menteri ATR/Waka BPN Surya Tjandra.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/299277/politikus-psi-raja-juli-antoni-tiba-di-istana-negara-bakal-jadi-wakil-menteri
tags: breaking news|jokowi|kabinet indonesia maju|psi|raja juli antoni|reshuffle kabinet|wakil menteri

title: Intip Harta Zulkifli Hasan dan Hadi Tjahjanto yang Akan Dilantik Jadi Menteri
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Politikus Zulkifli Hasan dan Mantan Panglima TNI Hadi Tjahjanto dikabarkan akan dilantik jadi menteri. ||||Isu reshuffle kabinet pun semakin menemukan titik terang setelah Hadi Tjahjanto muncul di Istana Negara pada Rabu (15/6/2022) pagi. ||||Ketua Umum Partai Amanat Nasional (PAN) Zulkifli Hasan yang dikabarkan akan menggantikan Muhammad Lutfi di posisi Mendag. ||||Hadi Tjahjanto juga dikabarkan akan jadi Menteri ATR/BPN.||||Baca Juga Perbandingan Harta Anies, Ganjar dan Prabowo Subianto, Siapa yang Terbesar? di https://www.kompas.tv/article/285959/perbandingan-harta-anies-ganjar-dan-prabowo-subianto-siapa-yang-terbesar||||Berapa harta kekayaan Zulkifli dan Hadi Tjahjanto yang tercatat pada E-LHKPN KPK?||||Pada  laporan tertanggal 20 april 2020/periodik  2019 Zulkifli hasan tertulis memiliki harta Rp 28.495.097.566.||||Sedangkan Hadi Tjahjanto pada laporan 18 maret 2020/periodik  2019 tercatat memiliki total harta Rp 20.249.498.294.||||Keduanya sama-sama tidak memiliki hutang, namun paling besar asset tercatat pada kepemilikan tanah dan bangunan. ||||Video Editor: Febi|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/299223/intip-harta-zulkifli-hasan-dan-hadi-tjahjanto-yang-akan-dilantik-jadi-menteri

title: Punched, Strangled: Nanny nabbed for torturing toddler in MP's Jabalpur, CCTV catches her red handed
description: A shocking video of a nanny hitting and manhandling a toddler in Madhya Pradesh's Jabalpur is now going viral. The nanny, identified as Rajini Chaudhury, was caught red-handed torturing a two-year-old boy. The parents of the child had hired a nanny to look after the child once they left for work. They noticed a change in their child and took him to a doctor, where it was found that the child's internal organs were swollen and it was suspected that he was tortured. After the change in the child's behaviour, followed by what the doctor said, the parents installed a CCTV camera, only to find out that the nanny they trusted was brutally assaulting their son. title: NEW McLaren Artura review: the SENSIBLE supercar?
description: Steve Sutcliffe drives the searingly fast McLaren Artura, and finds out that it could use just a little bit more bite...|Read more at Auto Express: |New 2022 McLaren Artura specs and details: https://aex.ae/33XkMry|The Artura matters for McLaren. A lot. Its new carbon fibre platform and twin-turbo V6 hybrid powertrain will form the basis for pretty much all McLarens for the next decade, so it canâ€™t really afford to put a foot wrong. Hence the reason its original launch was postponed from late last year until now, some eight months later, thereby allowing Ferrari to launch its own V6 hybrid â€“ the 296 GTB â€“ to such acclaim in the meantime. |But thatâ€™s how vital the Artura is to McLarenâ€™s future, so the fact that weâ€™ve now driven it in near-production form on its international launch and experienced numerous technical issues with it â€“ some minor, some not â€“ does seem hard to excuse. To be blunt, for all its speed, drama and dynamic capability, weâ€™re not sure it should be on sale just yet, not until thereâ€™s clear evidence that the technical issues it continues to suffer from have been resolved. This is not a nice thing to say about any new car, let alone one on which the future of a British car company is so obviously hinged. Nevertheless, we sent Steve Sutcliffe to find out what the new Artura is like on both road and track in this full review. |More Auto Express videos: |Car reviews playlist: http://aex.ae/2gY4ViX|Track battle playlist: https://aex.ae/2U8yvdf|Car news playlist: https://aex.ae/3vyKA8G|Follow us|Twitter: https://twitter.com/AutoExpress|Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AutoExpress|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/autoexpressmagazine

title: Jokowi Jengkel Sama Produk Impor: Bodoh Sekali, Saya Harus Ngomong Apa Adanya
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Kali ini Presiden Jokowi ngomong blak-blakan mengenai kondisi impor dalam negeri. ||||Jokowi menyesalkan kenapa APBN-APBD malah digunakan untuk membeli barang-barang impor. ||||"Jangan sampai kita ini memiliki APBN Rp 2.714 triliun, memiliki APBD Rp 1.197 triliun, belinya produk impor seperti tadi yang disampaikan Pak Kepala BPKP, bukan produk dalam negeri. Ini uang rakyat, uang yang dikumpulkan dari pajak, baik PPN, PPH badan, PPH perorangan, PPH karyawan, dari pihak ekspor, dari PNPB, dikumpulkan dengan cara yang tidak mudah, kemudian belanjanya belanja produk impor. Bodoh sekali kita,"tegas Jokowi saat Rapat Koordinasi Nasional Pengawasan Intern Pemerintah Tahun 2022 di Istana Merdeka, Jakarta Pusat, Selasa (14/6/2022).||||Baca Juga Di Tengah Isu Reshuffle, Jokowi Panggil Hadi Tjahjanto ke Istana Negara di https://www.kompas.tv/article/299100/di-tengah-isu-reshuffle-jokowi-panggil-hadi-tjahjanto-ke-istana-negara||||Jokowi heran kenapa barang impor yang dibeli merupakan uang yag berasal dari rakyat.||||"Maaf, kita ini pintar-pintar, tapi kalau caranya seperti itu, bodoh sekali kita. Saya harus ngomong apa adanya. Ini APBN loh, ini uang APBD loh, belinya produk impor. Nilai tambahnya yang dapat negara lain, lapangan kerja yang dapat orang lain, apa nggak bodoh kita ini,"lanjutnya. ||||Jokowi juga mengingat perjalanannya pada 5 tahun lalu terkait pipa ipor yang sebenarnya dalam negeri pun tersedia baik. ||||"Saya ke pabrik pipa, 'Semuanya ada Pak, Bapak mau cari apa ada, ukuran apa ada, kualitas apa ada. Ini kita ekspor semuanya Pak, ke Jepang, ke Amerika, ke Eropa. Lho, lho, lho, yang orang sana beli produk pipa kita malah kita beli impor. Sekali lagi, kita ini orang pinter-pinter, tapi melakukan hal yang sangat bodoh sekali,"tegasnya.||||Video Editor: Febi|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/299153/jokowi-jengkel-sama-produk-impor-bodoh-sekali-saya-harus-ngomong-apa-adanya

title: Dog wanders into store in Florida

title: Global National: June 14, 2022 | Questions swirl on Canada's move to pause vaccine travel mandates
description: On this episode of Global National: The Canadian government is suspending COVID-19 vaccine mandates for domestic and outbound international travellers starting June 20. Abigail Bimman explains why this won't shorten airport lineups, how the move is only temporary, and what pandemic protocols remain. Also, Dan Spector looks at why not everyone is on board with Ottawa's move, and what the tourism industry is hoping for.|Fears of flooding are rising high in Calgary and other parts of southern Alberta, as the city is under a local state of emergency due to heavy rain. Heather Yourex-West explains how this is bringing back painful memories of the 2013 disaster, and what makes this year different. Then, Global News meteorologist Tiffany LizÃ©e looks at what's in the forecast.|Plus, it's been a rough week for the cryptocurrency industry, as the value of Bitcoin and turmoil across major crypto platforms has left many investors worried about their digital wallets. Anne Gaviola takes a deeper look into the crypto "crash" and what it could mean going forward.| |And Canadian and Danish officials are raising a glass after settling a friendly, decades-long dispute over Hans Island, a tiny, obscure piece of land in the Arctic. Mike Drolet looks at what spurred the squabble, dubbed the "whisky war," and the solution.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8918505/covid-vaccine-requirement-planes-trains-canada/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #GlobalNational

title: College Inc. (full documentary) | FRONTLINE
description: FRONTLINE follows the money to uncover how Wall Street and a breed of for-profit universities transformed the way we think about college in America. (Aired 2010)|This journalism is made possible by viewers like you. Support your local PBS station here: http://www.pbs.org/donateâ€‹.|In â€œCollege, Inc.,â€ correspondent Martin Smith investigates the promise and explosive growth of the for-profit higher education industry. Through interviews with school executives, government officials, admissions counselors, former students, and industry observers, the documentary explores the tension between the industry â€” which says it's helping an underserved student population obtain a quality education and marketable job skills â€” and critics who charge the for-profits with churning out worthless degrees that leave students with a mountain of debt. At the center of it all stands a vulnerable population of potential students, often working adults eager for a university degree to move up the career ladder. |Love FRONTLINE? title: Ukraine pleads for more heavy weapons from West | DW News
description: Russian soldiers have surrounded the city of Sievierodonetsk. In a chemical plant in the city, Ukrainian soldiers are holding out, while some 500 civilians are believed to be sheltering inside, she added, recalling scenes from the Mariupol steel plant. Russian forces are also bombarding Sievierodonetsk's sister-city Lysychansk, where civilians were being taken in recent days. |Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy reiterated his urgent appeal for heavy weapons. In a statement on Tuesday, Zelenskyy expressed gratitude for what had been delivered so far, but that "it must come faster" if peace is to be achieved.|Russia's invasion of Ukraine has forced many countries to rethink their security and foreign policy. It's also helped unify western countries that often feuded with one another. That was especially the case in the European Union, which has had to find its way through multiple crises in the last decade.|Now Ukraine wants to join the bloc - and as soon as possible. Brussels is promising a quick decision on whether to award Ukraine candidate status - but that is only the first step in a long and complicated process. DW's Brussels correspondent Christine Mhundwa spoke to Ukraine's ambassador to the EU. title: Using Golf Clubs as Fishing Rods with Good Good Golf
description: In this episode of BlacktipH, we go offshore with our friends from Good Good Golf in search of fish! The day quickly began when we hooked up to a giant whoo- fighting it for almost 20 minutes before it sadly popped off. We moved on and caught some bonitos with live baits. Shortly after putting these baits out, we got a kingfish to bite! Jake fought it to the boat, and I gaffed it. We then moved north and dropped down the bonito we caught for some massive goliath groupers. title: Di Tengah Isu Reshuffle, Jokowi Panggil Hadi Tjahjanto ke Istana Negara
description: KOMPAS.TV - Di tengah kabar perombakan kabinet Indonesia Maju yang akan dilakukan Rabu 15 Juni besok, sejumlah tokoh menyambangi Istana Kepresidenan Jakarta sore tadi.||||Sejumlah tokoh yang datang ke Istana Presiden di antaranya eks Panglima TNI Panglima Hadi Tjahjanto.||||Baca Juga Presiden Panggil Zulkifli Hasan ke Istana di Tengah Isu Reshuffle di https://www.kompas.tv/article/299045/presiden-panggil-zulkifli-hasan-ke-istana-di-tengah-isu-reshuffle||||Tiba sekitar 18:00  tadi, Hadi Tjahjanto mengaku baru mendapat undangan dan belum mengetahui maksud pemanggilan.||||Selain Hadi Tjahjanto, Menteri Agraria dan Tata Ruang Sofyan Djalil juga dipanggil ke istana.||||Kemudian Menteri Pertahanan Prabowo Subianto, Wakil Menteri Agraria dan Tata Ruang Surya Candra, serta menteri perdagangan Muhammad Lutfhi dipanggil presiden.||||Di tengah isu perombakan cabinet, Partai Amanat Nasional (PAN) mengklaim salah satu kader terbaik akan memperoleh posisi menteri di Kabinet Joko Widodo - Ma'ruf Amin.||||Ketua DPP PAN Bima Arya mengaku jatah menteri yang bakal didapat oleh partainya berjumlah satu kursi.||||Ia pun mengatakan kader Partai Amanat Nasional siap mengisi posisi menteri mana pun.||||Bima Arya juga menyebut pan telah menyiapkan sejumlah kader. Namun nama-nama kandidat calon menteri telah dipegang oleh Ketua Umum PAN Zulkifli Hasan.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/299100/di-tengah-isu-reshuffle-jokowi-panggil-hadi-tjahjanto-ke-istana-negara
tags: hadi tjahjanto|isu reshuffle|jokowi|kabinet indonesia maju|pan|reshuffle

title: How We Retired Early With $2.2 Million To Travel The World
description: Dianne and Guillermo Rastelli retired at the ages 45 and 48 with $2.2 million and a plan to travel in search of their forever home. Dianne knew she had always wanted to retire before 50 and live in Colorado, but Guillermo, being Bolivian-American, told Dianne he was culturally raised with the idea that he should work as long and hard as he could to provide for his family. After a thoughtful presentation Dianne put together, Guillermo was convinced and even one-upped her idea and suggested they live in different countries around the world. title: Warriors snag Game 5 despite Steph Curry's cold-shooting vs. Jayson Tatum's Celtics | NBA | THE HERD
description: The Boston Celtics fell to the Golden State Warriors in Game 5 with a score of 104-94. Despite Steph Curry snapping his streak of 233 consecutive games with a three-pointer and shooting 22.5 percent from behind the arc and Jayson Tatum's 27 points, the Celtics could not get the job done. Boston committed 18 turnovers, 34 percent from the three-point line and just under 68 percent from the free throw line. Colin Cowherd shares his takeaways from Game 5, including why he believes the Celtics were a bit overwhelmed. On the other side, Curry finished with just 16 points (0-9 from three) and eight assists but the Warriors still prevailed. title: Andrew Wiggins shines, Warriors defeat Celtics in Game 5 of NBA Finals | NBA | UNDISPUTED

description: In a surprising turn of events, BMW is going to be launching its own 310cc supersport: the G 310 RR. It looks identical to the TVS Apache RR 310 but comes with a few additional goodies as standard. So, it begs the question, why is BMW rebadging the Apache and selling it as its own? title: Traffic congestion in Kuala Lumpur worsens as economy reopens, more return to office
description: Traffic congestion in Kuala Lumpur is back as Malaysia's economy reopens and more people return to workplaces. Data has shown the situation is worse than pre-pandemic levels. According to the road transport department, despite having a population of just over 33 million, there are over 30 million registered vehicles in Malaysia. On average , every household owns more than one car. Transport experts said contradictory car ownership policies, coupled with poor planning, are main reasons why public transport usage is far below the 40% targeted by the government. |Subscribe to our channel here: https://cna.asia/youtubesub ||||Subscribe to our news service on Telegram: https://cna.asia/telegram||||Follow us:||CNA: https://cna.asia||CNA Lifestyle: http://www.cnalifestyle.com ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/channelnewsasia||Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/channelnewsasia||Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/channelnewsasia

title: SUPRA SHOOTOUT: A80 vs A90 On The Top Gear Test Track | Stig's Garage ft. Becky Evans
description: IS THAT A SUPRA?! No - two actually. |The A80 Mk4 Supra was a supercar killer fresh out of the factory. Car magazines at the time pitched it against the Porsche 911 Turbo, the Ferrari Testarossa, and the Aston Martin DB7. That still didn't stop people over time from tuning these monsters through the roof thanks to that legendary 2JZ engine. The A80 was sadly withdrawn from all markets by 2002. But after a long hiatus of the Supra badge, we now have the latest-generation A90, developed in partnership with BMW.|How will the A90 GR Supra 3.0 Pro do against its predecessor around the Top Gear test track in the hands of The Stig? How close will Becky Evans's predictions be? Watch to find out... |MORE ABOUT TOP GEAR:|Want to watch a bit of Top Gear on the internet? Welcome to the most comprehensive collection of official clips you'll find on YouTube. title: Tent gemaakt van afgedankte onderbroeken | Klokko
description: CO2, weg ermee! Klokko presenteert een geheel CO2-neutrale vakantie. We noemen dit stukje land je ecologische voetafdruk. Door te reizen wordt je voetafdruk ook groter. Dat komt vooral omdat veel voertuigen vervuilende gassen uitstoten. Nizar zoekt uit hoe dat zit. Ook bezoekt hij wetenschappers die werken aan duurzamere manieren van reizen. title: Indian wheat in exchange for Indonesian palm oil? Modi govt mulls strategy to tame inflation
description: The Indian government is mulling a quid pro quo with Indonesian government to contain inflation back home. The Indian government has sought Indonesian palm oil imports in exchange for wheat export to meet rising food grain demand in Indonesia and to bring down the cooking oil prices in India. People familiar with the matter told Hindustan Times that India may permit export of wheat to meet Indonesiaâ€™s food grain demand through an arrangement where the Southeast Asian nation supplies palm oil without any interruption at a competitive rate to address Indiaâ€™s concerns over shortage of edible oil, one of the key factors powering inflation. The ministries of food and commerce are yet to respond to the development. Watch this video for more details.|#india #indonesia #wheat #palmoilindonesia #cookingoil #edibleoils #oil #modigovernment #modigovt #foodgrain #foodcrisis #world

title: Ridwan Kamil Potret Keindahan di Sekitar Makam Eril di Cimaung

Hatur Nuhun," tulis Ridwan Kamil.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298903/ridwan-kamil-potret-keindahan-di-sekitar-makam-eril-di-cimaung

title: Thane police website hacked over Prophet insult; Hacker wanted Modi govt to apologise to Muslims
description: The website of Thane police was briefly hacked today morning. Senior officer Sunil Lokhande said technical experts have recovered the data and the website has been restored. Lokhande added the hacking happened around 4am on Tuesday, and a probe in the regard was conducted by the cyber team of the Thane City Police. Meanwhile, additional director general of police (ADG) of Maharashtra Cyber Cell, Madhukar Pandey said that the hackers were traced to Malaysia and Indonesia. The hackers of Thane City Police's website claimed to be supporters of an Islamic group. Following the hacking, a message popped up on the website in which they demanded an immediate apology to â€œMuslims all over the worldâ€. Watch this video for more information.|#prophet #thanepolice #india #muslim #indiangovernment #modigovernment #modigovt #thane #hacker #hack #website #indonesia #malaysia

title: Russian forces cut off last routes out of Sievierodonetsk, Zelenskyy warns of 'brutal' battle
description: On Monday, Luhansk Governor Serhiy Haidai said the Russian military destroyed all bridges connecting the city, making civilian evacuations and humanitarian aid deliveries nearly impossible. |Oleksandr Stryuk, the head of the Sievierodonetsk city administration, said that "massive shelling" destroyed a third bridge in the key eastern Ukrainian city, "but the city is not isolated. There are communication channels even if they are quite complicated," Stryuk told Ukrainian television. He said Ukrainian forces "continue to defend the city" after the bridge over the Siverskyi Donets River, linking the city to Ukrainian-controlled Lysychansk, was destroyed. |The British Defense Ministry said in its regular intelligence report that Russian forces likely made "small advances" in the northeastern Kharkiv for the first time in weeks. The report added that the city of Sievierodonetsk in the eastern Donbas region remains the main focus of Russia in its war in Ukraine. According to the ministry, Russia's defense industry could struggle to meet the "demands" arising from the war in Ukraine, "partially due to the effects of sanctions and lack of expertise."|The report noted that a top Russian defense official had recently predicted that defense spending would see a 20% increase, around 700 billion rubles (around â‚¬11 billion, $12 billion). It said such funding is allowing Russia's "defense industrial base to be slowly mobilized to meet demands placed on it by the war in Ukraine. Russia's production of high-quality optics and advanced electronics likely remain troubled and could undermine its efforts to replace equipment lost in Ukraine," the report added. |German Chancellor Olaf Scholz spoke before his meeting with Slovak Prime Minister Eduard Heger and reiterated Berlin's commitment to supply Ukraine with modern weaponry. "It is clear that Ukraine needs additional weapons for its defense," Scholz said, adding that Germany has supplied Ukraine with arms since the start of the invasion. "In this critical phase we are considerably expanding our support: we will supply Ukraine with a state-of-the-art anti-aircraft system and an artillery detection radar, among other things," the chancellor went on to say. Scholz said that the arms would be supplied in coordination with European and NATO partners. He added that it was important that Germany and its allies defend "every square inch of NATO territory," and that Berlin would increase its presence on NATO's eastern flank. Earlier, Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy criticized Scholz and German officials in an interview with the ZDF broadcaster, and urged Berlin not to prioritize its relations with Russia over Ukraine's defense.|"We need from Chancellor Scholz the certainty that Germany supports Ukraine," he said. "He and his government must decide: there can't be a trade-off between Ukraine and relations with Russia."|Scholz has countered criticism that Germany was being slow in delivering heavy weapons to Ukraine, arguing that Ukraine's soldiers must first receive training to use such advanced weapons. "This is about really heavy equipment. You have to be able to use that, you have to be trained for that," Scholz said, adding that Ukrainian forces were currently undergoing training in Germany. |Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #Sievierodonetsk

title: 2023 Land Rover Range Rover - Extraordinary Large Luxury SUV!
description: Special thanks to: Al Ain Class Motors|https://www.instagram.com/alainclassmotors/|https://www.alainclass.com/|2023 Land Rover Range Rover|Starting at $105.850|    Highs Elegant exterior styling, sumptuously-outfitted cabin, range of powerful and polished powertrains.|    Lows Six-figure starting price, plug-in hybrid only offered on base trim, snug third-row headroom.|    Verdict Suave, sophisticated, and sybaritic, the 2023 Range Rover is everything a flagship luxury SUV should be.|Overview|What attracts global elites to the Range Rover isn't the SUV's legendary off-road capability, but rather its effortlessly elegant styling, its opulent cabin, and the A-list status that itâ€™s developed over the years. The list of Range Rover owners even includes Her Majesty the Queen. One couldn't ask for a better brand ambassador. The 2023 model represents the most luxurious Range Rover yet. A trio of powertrain optionsâ€”including a hybridâ€”deliver ample power; the brand's largest SUV comports itself through traffic regally, with a smooth ride and a hushed interior. Venturing off-road is certainly an option for Range Rover owners; all-wheel drive is standard and the air suspension can be raised to provide extra ground clearanceâ€”although we know that few will actually dare to subject this rolling art piece to such indignity. The Range Rover starts at over $100,000, which means it's more expensive than rivals such as the Cadillac Escalade, the Jeep Grand Wagoneer, and the Mercedes-Benz GLS-class. So be it. The Rangeâ€™s reputation, presence, and royal endorsement all help justify its premium price tag. |What's New for 2023?|The revamped Range Rover technically debuted for the 2022 model year, but it was confusingly sold alongside the previous generation model, and not all of its variants were available. For 2023, the older model is no more. For 2023 the plug-in hybrid P440e powertrain joins the lineup, and Land Rover says this setup will provide up to 48 miles of electric-only driving range. It's available exclusively on the short-wheelbase SE trim.|Pricing and Which One to Buy|SE: $105,850|SE PHEV: $106,250|Autobiography: $158,950|First Edition: $165,350|SV: $194,450|We'd recommend opting for the mid-range Autobiography model, which adds several sought-after items that luxury buyers will appreciate. For example, the Autobiography comes standard with a 1600-watt Meridian stereo system featuring headrest-mounted speakers and active noise cancellation. The Range Rover will be offered in both a short- and long-wheelbase body styles; and we suggest going for the latter since it creates room for a third row of seats and provides a more generous cargo area.|Engine, Transmission, and Performance|The Range Rover is available with a trio of powertrains, starting with a turbocharged inline-six with a 48-volt hybrid system dubbed P400 that develops 395 horsepower. During our initial test drive it proved to be silky-smooth and provided adequate pep to tug the large Range Rover around. A 523-hp twin-turbo 4.4-liter V-8 engineâ€”Land Rover calls it P530â€”is even perkier and cranks up the Range Rover's towing capacity to 8200 pounds. A 434-hp plug-in hybrid optionâ€”called P440eâ€”is also available but only on the short wheelbase SE trim. The Range Rover's ride is suitably plush and, with its adjustable air suspension set to Comfort mode, it virtually floats down the road. Turning the dial to Dynamic mode firms things up some, but the big Rover still aims for a comfort-first mission. When we get a chance to take the Range Rover on our test track, we'll update this story with test results.|Range, Charging, and Battery Life|The EPA hasn't released official range estimates for the plug-in hybrid P440e, but Land Rover says the system's 31.8-kWh battery pack should provide around 48 miles of electric-only driving range. The P440e is capable of DC fast charging or can be charged at a home-based charger.|Read More https://www.caranddriver.com/land-rover/range-rover|ğŸ“Œ Instagram â–¶ https://www.instagram.com/cartvpress|ğŸ“Œ Facebook  â–¶ https://www.facebook.com/CARTVPress

title: Crispy Healthy Lauki Vadi Snack - Doodhi Tea Time Nastha Recipe | Quick & Easy Bottle Gourd Handwo
description: full recipe: https://hebbarskitchen.com/lauki-vadi-recipe-crispy-healthy/|Lauki vadi recipe | Crispy & Healthy Dhudhi Snack | Bottle Gourd Fritters with detailed photo and video recipe. Basically an extension of the popular alu vadi recipe prepared with bottled gourd vegetables. It is healthy, crispy and more importantly very lite and does not feel filling even though it is made with besan and eventually deep-fried. These deep-fried snacks can be easily consumed as it is but tastes great when served with a generous amount of green chutney or tomato ketchup sauce.|Lauki vadi recipe | Crispy & Healthy Dhudhi Snack | Bottle Gourd Fritters with step-by-step photo and video recipe. Vadi or crispy deep-fried fritters are super special in western Indian cuisine. It is typically served as simple side snacks for lunch and dinner, if not as tea time snack, but it has a lot of applications. Generally, it is prepared with leafy vegetables like arbi leaves, but can also be prepared with vegetables and lauki vadi recipe is one such hugely popular snack meal.|#hebbarskitchen

title: First flight taking asylum seekers from UK to Rwanda due to take off - BBC News
description: The first flight taking asylum seekers to Rwanda will take off and people who are not removed on Tuesday will be on subsequent flights, UK's Foreign Secretary Liz Truss has said.|Seven or eight people are due to be removed on Tuesday, after dozens won legal cases to be taken off. But more legal challenges are set to be heard.|Three more legal challenges from people set to be flown to the east African nation's capital Kigali are expected to be heard in the courts before the flight departs.|A last-ditch attempt to block the flight altogether was rejected by the Court of Appeal on Monday, however.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: Potret Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Praratya Ziarah ke Makam Eril
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil dan istrinya, Atalia Praratya berziarah ke makam Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril pada Selasa, 14 Juni 2022 pagi.||||Mereka mendatangi Komplek Islamic Centre Baitul Ridwan di Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung.||||Usai berziarah keluarga Ridwan Kamil sempat menyapa warga yang berada di pintu gerbang.||||Baca Juga Warga Ikuti Pemakaman Eril Putra Sulung Ridwan Kamil di Cimaung di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298755/warga-ikuti-pemakaman-eril-putra-sulung-ridwan-kamil-di-cimaung||||Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz dimakamkan pada Senin, 13 Juni 2022 pagi.||||Ridwan Kamil dalam prosesi pemakaman kemarin, meminta dibukakan pintu maaf untuk Eril.||||"Kami memohon dibukakan pintu maaf kepada almarhum Ananda Emmeril jika selama hidupnya ada ucapan, ada tindakan, ada hal yang kurang berkenan. Kami mohon dibukakan pintu maaf atas kekhilafan dan dosanya," ucapnya.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298819/potret-ridwan-kamil-dan-atalia-praratya-ziarah-ke-makam-eril

title: Jokowi Cerita Ada Perdana Menteri Mengemis Minta Dikirimi Minyak Goreng
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Jokowi menceritakan ada Perdana Menteri dari sebuah negara yang tak mau disebutkannya meminta-minta dikirimi minyak goreng dari Indonesia.||||Hal ini Presiden Jokowi sampaikan di Istana Negara pada 14 Juni 2022.||||Baca Juga Jokowi Mau Reshuffle Kabinet 15 Juni? Istana Menyebut soal Kebutuhan Kabinet Saat Ini di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298797/jokowi-mau-reshuffle-kabinet-15-juni-istana-menyebut-soal-kebutuhan-kabinet-saat-ini||||"Dua hari yang lalu malam, saya mendapatkan telepon dari seorang perdana menteri ga usah saya sebutkan beliau meminta-minta betul, Presiden Jokowi tolong dalam sehari dua hari ini kirim yang namanya minyak goreng," ujar Jokowi dalam sambutannya pada Pembukaan Rapat Koordinasi Nasional Pengawasan Intern Pemerintah Tahun 2022, Selasa (14/6/2022).||||"Beliau meminta-minta betul, 'Presiden Jokowi, tolong dalam sehari-dua hari ini kirim yang namanya minyak goreng. Stok kami betul-betul sudah habis. Kalau barang ini tidak datang, akan terjadi krisis sosial, ekonomi, berujung pada krisis politik,'," kata Jokowi.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298836/jokowi-cerita-ada-perdana-menteri-mengemis-minta-dikirimi-minyak-goreng

title: Indian military to create â€˜Agniveerâ€™ rank for new recruits in all three services | Key Details
description: The Government is likely to announce the Agnipath recruitment scheme for the defence forces today. Under the Agnipath recruitment scheme, troops would be recruited only for four-year tenures. Soldiers recruited under the new model will be inducted in the armed forces as â€˜Agniveersâ€™, a new distinct rank, as opposed to sepoys who joined the Indian Army under the legacy recruitment model. â€˜Agniveersâ€™ will form a distinct rank in all three services, and will also wear a distinct insignia as part of their uniform. The announcement will set the stage for the army to restart its recruitment process after a two-year freeze caused by Covid-19 restrictions. title: EU angered by Britain's plans for unilateral changes in post-Brexit trade rules | DW News
description: The British government on Monday introduced a bill to Parliament on amendments to the post-Brexit rules that govern trade with Northern Ireland. The European Union says it will respond with all measures at its disposal if Britain pushes ahead with unilateral changes to the Brexit deal on Northern Ireland. It has said any changes would breach international law. Following the announcement, the EU warned that it could launch "infringement procedures" against the UK.|Earlier in the day, UK Foreign Secretary Liz Truss said London wanted a "negotiated solution" to the issue with Brussels and denied that the move was illegal. The UK government had remained quiet about the details of its plan but said they will be "lawful and correct." Johnson himself said the changes would help ease pro-British unionist concerns over the Brexit deal.|US Secretary of State Antony Blinken urged the UK to continue "good-faith negotiations" with the EU in a call with Liz Truss later on Monday, the US State Department said.|What changes have been mentioned?|The proposed changes include the setting up of a "green channel" for goods moving from Britain to Northern Ireland that are destined to stay in the UK. Goods being sent further to the EU would be directed to a "red channel." The UK government has promised penalties for those who try to abuse the system and take advantage of the EU's single market from the UK. They are expected to eliminate European Union state aid rules on subsidies provided to businesses by public authorities in the province.|UK government ministers have also previously said that they wish to no longer allow the European Court of Justice to be the sole arbiter of any disputes, arguing that British courts should have some role.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Brexit #Backstop #NorthernIrelandProtocol

title: Ridwan Kamil dan Keluarga Kembali Ziarah ke Makam Eril, Warga Diperbolehkan Ziarah Sepekan ke Depan
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga, pagi ini berziarah ke makam putra sulungnya, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril di Kompleks Islamic Center Baitul Ridwan Desa Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Usai ziarah, Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga sempat menyapa warga yang berada di pintu gerbang lokasi pemakaman.||||Jadwal ziarah ke makam Eril untuk warga akan dibuka mulai jam 08.00 pagi hingga jam pukul 17.00 sore.||||Baca Juga Warga Ikuti Pemakaman Eril Putra Sulung Ridwan Kamil di Cimaung di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298755/warga-ikuti-pemakaman-eril-putra-sulung-ridwan-kamil-di-cimaung||||Ziarah yang diperuntukan bagi warga akan diberlakukan selama 1 pekan ke depan.||||Sementara, masyarakat ada yang sudah mulai melakukan ziarah ke makam eril di Komplek Islamic Center Baitul Ridwan di Desa Cimaung.||||Pengunjung ziarah dibatasi hanya 10 orang dan waktu ziarah 10 menit untuk mengantisipasi penumpukan di area makam.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298821/ridwan-kamil-dan-keluarga-kembali-ziarah-ke-makam-eril-warga-diperbolehkan-ziarah-sepekan-ke-depan

title: Jokowi Geram Banyak Kementerian hingga Daerah Kerap Belanja Produk Impor
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Presiden Joko Widodo mengatakan banyak kementerian, lembaga hingga daerah yang tidak mau menggunakan produk dalam negeri.||||Hal ini disampaikan Jokowi saat membuka rapat Koordinasi Nasional Pengawasan Intern Pemerintah Tahun 2022 di Istana Negara pada Selasa (14/6)||||Dalam kesempatan itu, Jokowi sampaikan alasan berbagai pihak cukup beragam, mulai dari spek hingga kualitas yang dinilai tidak baik.||||Baca Juga Presiden Jokowi Reshuffle Menteri Besok? Ini Kata Istana! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298855/presiden-jokowi-reshuffle-menteri-besok-ini-kata-istana||||"Beli impor yang saya cek, beli impor. Alasannya ada saja 'Kualitasnya Pak, speknya Pak enggak pas'. Kayak kita ini enggak ngerti masalah spesifikasi," ujar dia.||||Ia ingatkan kondisi seperti ini harus diawasi, Jokowi juga meminta agar pengawasan dilakukan dengan baik sehingga dapat memacu pertumbuhan ekonomi dan lapangan kerja yang semakin banyak.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298879/jokowi-geram-banyak-kementerian-hingga-daerah-kerap-belanja-produk-impor

title: Presiden Jokowi Reshuffle Menteri Besok? Ini Kata Istana!
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Santer terdengar isu Reshuffle Kabinet Presiden Jokowi yang akan dilakukan pada Rabu, 15 Juni 2022.||||Sekretaris Kabinet Pramono Anung pun buka suara soal isu Reshuffle Kabinet atau perombakan  kabinet pada 15 Juni 2022 ini.||||Pramono Anung menyebut perombakan kabinet merupakan hak prerogatif dari Presiden Jokowi.||||Baca Juga Jokowi Cerita Ada Perdana Menteri Mengemis Minta Dikirimi Minyak Goreng di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298836/jokowi-cerita-ada-perdana-menteri-mengemis-minta-dikirimi-minyak-goreng||||"Jadi yang namanya kabinet itu kewenangan sepenuhnya presiden. Presiden itu mempunyai hak prerogatif. Presiden mau ganti kapan aja ya terserah presiden. Mau hari ini, mau besok, mau lusa. Rapi kewenangan itu sepenuhnya ada pada presiden," kata Pramono kepada wartawan, di Kompleks Istana Merdeka, Jakarta, Selasa (14/6/2022).||||"Ya yang jelas presiden kan beliau sudah 8 tahun di pemerintahan ini dan beliau tahu banget mana yang menjadi kebutuhan dari kabinet ini. Sehingga itu yang menjadi.. beliau sangat tahu lah," ujarnya.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298855/presiden-jokowi-reshuffle-menteri-besok-ini-kata-istana

title: Nadzar - Sahabatku Kekasihmu (Official Music Video)
description: Dengarkan Nadzar - Sahabatku Kekasihmu di music streaming: https://lnkfi.re/SahabatkuKekasihmu|Gimana nih rasanya bestie kamu ternyata menyukai kekasihmu, hal apa yang akan kamu lakukan dengan sahabat dan kekasihmu? koment dibawah yuk!|Jangan lupa untuk like, subscribe dan share ke teman-teman sosmed kalian ya.|Press Release|ARTIS  : NADZAR BAND|LAPGU  : SAHABATKU KEKASIHMU|CIPTAAN : ATO ANGKASA|LABEL  : GP RECORDS|NADZAR BAND adalah kumpulan anak muda asal kota Cianjur, Jawa Barat. Yang memiliki visi misi satu pandangan yang sama dalam bermain musik dan nama Nadzar sendiri berarti Janji. Band yang dibentuk pada 31 Desember 2014 dengan formasi Uky (Vokalis), TomTom (Gitaris), Rara (Bassist) dan Aldy (Drummers), mengusung genre Alternative Rock.|Bicara soal pengalaman, Nadzar bisa disebut Band yang merajai festival di daerahnya cianjur dan Jawa Barat. Selain itu, Nadzar pernah dipercaya satu panggung bersama legenda Rock Indonesia yaitu Achmad Albar. |"Nadzar bagi kita itu adalah keluarga tidak hanya sekedar bermain musik, lika-liku perjalanan selama kami bermusik banyak cerita yang kita alami bersama pastinya" Ucap Tomtom.|Pada Tahun 2022, menjadi awal karir Nadzar untuk meramaikan industri musik Indonesia dengan mengeluarkan sebuah lagu yang berjudul â€œSAHABATKU KEKASIHMUâ€ Ciptaan  Ato Angkasa di bawah naungan label musik GP Records.|Lagu Sahabatku Kekasihmu bercerita tentang sebuah persahabatan, perselingkuhan dan kesetiaan. untuk aransement musiknya dibuat easy listening, meski lagu ini memiliki tempo sedikit cepat akan tetap enak untuk didengarkan. |Dalam video klip lagu Sahabatku Kekasihmu, kita akan mendapatkan pesan yang bagus yaitu tentang arti sebuah persahabatan yang diperankan langsung oleh personil Nadzar Band. Uky sang vokalis diceritakan memiliki seorang kekasih, namun kekasihnya tersebut malah mencoba untuk mendekati Tom Tom yaitu sahabat kekasihnya. Walau sempat tergoda, namun Tom Tom cepat sadar bahwa hal tersebut salah dan akan berimbas kepada persahabatannya dengan Uky. |Nadzar tentunya sangat berharap lagu â€œSahabatku Kekasihmuâ€ dapat diterima dengan baik oleh seluruh lapisan masyarakat. dukungan dan doa tentunya sangat diharapkan dari teman â€“ teman media cetak, online, elektronik, dll. Sehingga apa yang jadi tujuan Nadzar bisa terwujud.|SALAM MUSIK INDONESIA|Lirik lagu Sahabatku Kekasihmu|Ini bukanlah mimpi|Ini kenyataan hati|Tak habis ku berfikir|Kau bisa dengan dia |Kau lihat, dia lihat|Kau senyum,dia senyum|Kurasa ada yang berbeda|Dari kalian|Reff : |Dia sahabat ku,Dia temanku|Tak kusangka|Kau bermain cinta|Dan ternyata kau berdua jalani cinta|Sakitnya hatiku|Perihnya jiwaku|Hianatiku dengan rencanamu|Tak kusangka, tak kuduga|Dengan sahabatku|Dia sahabatku|Dia temanku|Dia sahabatku... title: Russia pushes Saudi Arabia to third place to become India's second-biggest oil exporter in May
description: Russia overtakes Saudi Arabia to become India's 2nd biggest oil supplier behind Iraq as refiners snap up Russian crude available at a deep discount following the war in Ukraine. Industry data shows that Indian refiners bought about 25 million barrels of Russian oil in May, or more than 16 per cent of all their oil imports. Russian-origin crude hit 5 per cent of Indiaâ€™s total seaborne imports in April for the first time, rising from under 1% throughout 2021 and Q1 2022, the data showed. India, the worldâ€™s third-biggest oil-importing and consuming nation, has long defended purchases of crude oil from Russia as it is minuscule in comparison to Indiaâ€™s total consumption. title: Polisi Tangkap Menteri Pendidikan Khilafatul Muslimin, Perannya Sebarkan Doktrin Paham Khilafah!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Terbaru, Polda Metro Jaya kembali menangkap 1 anggota Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Di Pondok Pesantren di Kota Mojokerto inilah diduga jadi lokasi penangkapan anggota Khilafatul, Senin (13/6/2022) dini hari, pukul 00.30 WIB.||||Pria yang ditangkap berperan sebagai Menteri Pendidikan Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Ia bertugas memberi doktrin tentang paham Khilafah, termasuk ke sejumlah sekolah.||||Sebelumnya, pasca penangkapan sejumlah pengurus Khilafatul Muslimin di Bandar Lampung, Tim Gabungan Polisi dan TNI serta Pemerintah Daerah menertibkan plang Kantor Pusat Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Baca Juga Samin Tan Tetap Divonis Bebas, Majelis Kasasi: Ia Tak Terbukti Atas Dakwaan Jaksa! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298728/samin-tan-tetap-divonis-bebas-majelis-kasasi-ia-tak-terbukti-atas-dakwaan-jaksa||||Pencopotan plang Khilafatul Muslimin dilakukan di 14 lokasi, 5 Kecamatan Kota Bandar Lampung.||||Pencopotan plang ini merupakan buntut dari ditangkapnya sejumlah petinggi Khilafatul Muslimin beberapa hari lalu.||||Menurut polisi, plang tidak memiliki izin pasang.||||Di Indramayu, plang nama Kantor Cabang Khilafatul Muslimin Kemasulan Karangampel di Jalan Raya Kaplongan, Kecamatan Karangampel, Kabupaten Indramayu, Jawa Barat juga di copot.||||Ini dilakukan mandiri oleh pengurus guna menciptakan suasana kondusif.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298738/polisi-tangkap-menteri-pendidikan-khilafatul-muslimin-perannya-sebarkan-doktrin-paham-khilafah
tags: khilafah|khilafatul muslimin|menteri pendidikan khilafatul muslimin|organisasi menyimpang agama|paham khilafah|pimpinan khilafatul muslimin ditangkap

title: Why Johnny Depp Is RETURNING to Court
description: Johnny Depp is heading back to court following his trial victory against ex-wife Amber Heard. The actor faces a civil suit for assault, following an alleged physical altercation in 2018. According to court docs obtained by ET, a crew member on his movie, 'City of Lies,' alleges Depp punched him twice on the set.

title: Petinggi Khilafatul Muslimin di Bekasi Ditangkap Saat Dagang Mie Ayam
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Kepolisian Polda Metro Jaya kembali melakukan penangkapan terhadap beberapa pimpinan Khilafatul Muslimin di beberapa daerah.||||satu diantaranya di kota bekasi. Yakni sosok SW yang merupakan salah satu petinggi Khilafatul di tangkap di kawasan Bekasi Selatan, Kota Bekasi, Jawa Barat.||||SW ditangkap di lokasi usahanya yaitu Mie Ayam. Saat disambangi usaha Mie Ayam ini masih beraktifitas berjualan. Karena SW ini membuka usaha bersama salah satu rekannya bernama Wito Abdurahman||||Baca Juga Kata Gibran soal Adanya Kantor Khilafatul Muslim di Solo di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298753/kata-gibran-soal-adanya-kantor-khilafatul-muslim-di-solo||||Wito Abdurahman membenarkan adanya penangkapan SW, namun saat ditangkap dirinya sudah pulang lebih awal karena dalam berjualan mie ayam dirinya berbagi waktu pagi dan siang. Sejauh ini dirinya masih kebingungan terkait penangkapan tersebut terkait dalam hal apa. Ia juga belum lama mengenal sosok SW karena baru kurang lebih tiga sampai empat tahun.||||Sementara itu, Amir Khilafah Muslimin Bekasi Raya Abu Salma yang membawahi Bekasi, Depok dan Bogor mengatakan bahwa sosok SW  adalah pendiri dari khilafah dan tertulis dalam akte pendirian.||||Video Editor: Febi Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298786/petinggi-khilafatul-muslimin-di-bekasi-ditangkap-saat-dagang-mie-ayam

title: Israel covertly hunting Iran's Revolutionary Guards? Now IRGC loses two aerospace personnel
description: Two members of Iran's aerospace industry who were on unspecified missions have died amid controversy over the country's nuclear programme. The cases are the latest in a string of mysterious deaths, many of which have been linked to Israel. The labelling of both deaths as 'martyrdoms' possibly indicates that Iran believes the men to have been killed. Weeks back, Iran vowed to avenge these mysterious killings and claimed that Israel is behind several sabotage attacks on its nuclear and military sites. Tensions between the two archenemies have significantly escalated in the past few months as Israel continues to warn that Iran is advancing towards building a nuclear bomb while Tehran claims its nuclear programme is strictly peaceful. Full detail in this report.|#israel #iran #iraneliteguard #irannuclearprogramme #nuclearbomb #nuclear #tehran #tehrannews #mossad #revolutionaryguard #irgc #mysterious #killing

title: Ina Garten's Penne Arrabiata | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network
description: Ina slow cooks her garlic in olive oil for a sweet and delicious addition to this elegant, make-ahead pasta sauce!|Subscribe to #discoveryplus to stream more of #BarefootContessa: http://discoverypl.us/2NeKVgd|Get the recipe â–¶ https://foodtv.com/3ztMSeM|Subscribe to Food Network â–¶ http://foodtv.com/YouTube|Ina throws open the doors of her Hamptons home for delicious food, dazzling entertaining ideas and good fun on Barefoot Contessa.|Welcome to Food Network, where learning to cook is as simple as clicking play! Grab your apron and get ready to get cookin' with some of the best chefs around the world. We'll give you a behind-the-scenes look at our best shows, take you inside our favorite restaurant and be your resource in the kitchen to make sure every meal is a 10/10!|Penne Arrabiata|RECIPE COURTESY OF INA GARTEN|Level: Easy|Total: 1 hr 5 min|Active: 30 min|Yield: 4 to 5 servings|Ingredients|2/3 cup good olive oil|1 cup whole peeled garlic cloves (24 cloves) |2 (28-ounce) cans whole peeled San Marzano tomatoes |2 teaspoons whole fennel seeds, chopped |1 teaspoon crushed red pepper flakes |1/3 cup dry red wine, such as Chianti |Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper|1/4 cup julienned fresh basil leaves, plus extra for serving |1 pound dry penne rigate, such as DeCecco |Freshly grated Parmesan cheese, for serving |Directions|In a medium (10-inch) pot or Dutch oven, such as Le Creuset, warm the olive oil over medium-low heat. Add the garlic and cook for 10 to 12 minutes, tossing occasionally, until the garlic has softened and is lightly browned.|Meanwhile, drain the tomatoes, place them in a food processor fitted with the steel blade, and pulse until they're roughly chopped. With a slotted spoon, transfer the garlic to the food processor and pulse again to chop the garlic. Pour the tomato mixture into the pot with the olive oil, add the fennel, red pepper flakes, red wine, 1 tablespoon salt, and 1 teaspoon black pepper. Bring to a boil, lower the heat, and simmer for 30 minutes. Stir in the basil, taste for seasonings (it will be very spicy!), and keep warm over very low heat.|Meanwhile, bring a large pot of water to a full boil. Add 2 tablespoons kosher salt and the penne and cook according to the directions of the package.|Two minutes before the pasta is al dente, using a wire or spider strainer, lift the pasta out of the boiling water and add it to the sauce, along with 1/4 cup of the pasta water. Simmer for 2 to 3 minutes, until the pasta is al dente. Spoon the pasta into low shallow bowls, sprinkle with extra basil and Parmesan cheese, and serve hot.|Subscribe to our channel to fill up on the latest must-eat recipes, brilliant kitchen hacks and content from your favorite Food Network shows.|â–¶ FOOD NETWORK KITCHEN APP: http://foodtv.com/FNKApp|â–¶ WEBSITE: https://www.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FULL EPISODES: https://watch.foodnetwork.com|â–¶ FACEBOOK: https://www.facebook.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/FoodNetwork|â–¶ TWITTER: https://twitter.com/FoodNetwork|#InaGarten #BarefootContessa #FoodNetwork #PenneArrabiata |Ina Garten's Penne Arrabiata | Barefoot Contessa | Food Network|https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tiy7i6uc960

description: Resident Evil Village is returning with brand new DLC. Set 16 years after the events of Resident Evil Village, Ethan Winters' daughter, Rosemary, returns to the village to find answers. title: Spider-Man: Across The Spider-Verse Reveals Two New Spidey Villains - IGN The Fix: Entertainment
description: New Spider-Man villains have been revealed for Spider-Man: Across The Spider-Verse! Revealed at the Annecy International Film Festival over the weekend and shared on the official Spider-Verse Twitter handle, we see Miles and Gwen take on The Spot. According to the post, The Spot is not only a deep cut into the #SpiderMan rogue's gallery, but apparently one of his most formidable foes to-date. The Spot will be voiced by actor Jason Schwartzman. But he's not the only villain making an appearance. The Vulture will be swooping in to wreak havoc within the Spider-Verse, voiced by Jorma Taccone from The Lonely Island of SNL fame. More Marvel news sees us laying down the hammer on these new Thor Love and Thunder character posters. And finally, Netflix revealed the title for Knives Out 2, 'Glass Onion: A Knives Out Mystery'.|#IGN #SpiderMan #Marvel

title: Capcom Showcase 2022 Full Presentation
description: Today during Capcom's Showcase for Summer of 2022 we learned more about Monster Hunter Rise Sunbreak, as well as new information and exo suits in EXOPRIMAL, and finally we got updates across the Resident Evil Franchise. First we got to see Shadows of Roses the DLC for Resident Evil Village, as well as updates to Mercenaries Mode including the ability to play as Lady Dimitrescu. After that we got updates on Resident Evil 4 the remake which showed off 15 seconds of brand new gameplay. title: WATCH: Giulianiâ€™s false claim of â€˜suitcase full of ballotsâ€™ debunked by former U.S. attorney
description: BJay Pak, a former U.S. Attorney for the Northern District of Georgia, testified on June 13 as the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack presented its findings to the public.|Pak said that former Attorney General Bill Barr asked him to investigate claims made by Rudy Giuliani about election fraud in Atlanta, Georgia, which included an allegation that ballots had been put in a suitcase.|â€œUnfortunately, during the Senate hearing, Mr. Giuliani only played a clip that showed them pulling out the official ballot box from under the table and referring to that as a smoking gun of fraud in Fulton County, when in actuality in review of the entire video, it showed that that was an official ballot box kept underneath the table,â€ Pak said.|â€œThe FBI interviewed the individuals depicted in the videos that purportedly were triple-counting the ballots and determined nothing irregular happened in the counting and the allegations made by Mr. Giuliani were false,â€ he added.|The hearing was the second of several planned by the Jan. 6 committee that focused on how Trump actively spread false information about the 2020 election outcome â€“ what has become known as the â€œbig lieâ€ â€“ in the run up to the Jan. 6 insurrection. In the year since its creation, the committee has conducted more than 1,000 interviews, seeking critical information and documents from people witness to, or involved in, the violence that day.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG|Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6|Follow us:|Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour|Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour

title: WATCH: â€˜Trump campaign did not make its caseâ€™ in court, GOP election attorney testifies
description: Republican attorney Benjamin Ginsberg, an expert in election law who played a key role in the 2000 Florida recount, testified on June 13 as the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack presented its findings to the public.|Ginsberg weighed in to explain how former President Donald Trumpâ€™s campaign strategy defied the normal process for post-election litigation. He also noted that Trumpâ€™s first problem was that the 2020 election really was not close, and that recounts could not have changed the outcome.|Ginsberg said Trumpâ€™s campaign had dozens of opportunities to legally challenge the election results, despite its complaint that it did not have its day in court.|â€œAbout half of those cases â€¦ were dismissed at the procedural stage,â€ he said. In cases that were not immediately dismissed, â€œin no instance did a court find that the charges of fraud were real,â€ he added.|Ginsberg said post-election reviews in the six battleground states, including the â€˜somewhat farcicalâ€™ Cyber Ninjaâ€™s case in Arizona, found no credible evidence of fraud.|The hearing was the second of several planned by the Jan. 6 committee that focused on how Trump actively spread false information about the 2020 election outcome â€“ what has become known as the â€œbig lieâ€ â€“ in the run up to the Jan. 6 insurrection. In the year since its creation, the committee has conducted more than 1,000 interviews, seeking critical information and documents from people witness to, or involved in, the violence that day.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG|Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6|Follow us:|Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour|Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour

title: Ukraine says civilians under fire in Sievierodonetsk chemical plant | DW News
description: The Azot chemical plant, where hundreds of civilians from the embattled town of Sievierodonetsk have sought refuge, has come under fire from Russian artillery, regional governor Serhiy Haidai said on Monday.|Russian forces have also made advances in the city, now controlling about 70% according to Haidai.|"Russians continue to storm the city, having a significant advantage in artillery they have somewhat pushed back the Ukrainian soldiers," he said on social media.|"About 500 civilians remain on the grounds of the Azot plant in Sievierodonetsk, 40 of them are children. Sometimes the military manages to evacuate someone," the regional governor added.|The capture of Sievierodonetsk would open up the way for Russian troops to advance on other key towns in the region.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#Ukraine #Russia #Sievierodonetsk

title: Diablo 4 Necromancer, PvP, World Boss Gameplay
description: We got our hands on some extra gameplay footage of Diablo 4 hot off the new Necromancer announcement and Diablo IV gameplay showcase at the Xbox & Bethesda Games showcase. Jake and Erick talk about some of the gameplay to see what extra things they can learn about the Necromancer, PvP and also a World Boss.|We get a deeper dive on some of the Necromancer's skills especially the "Book of Dead" which seems to be its summoning skills. We learn there are three skills shown off including Skeletal Warriors, Skeletal Mages, and Golem. This information below is subject to change as this is not a final build but here is what we saw from the gameplay regarding the 3 various summons. Each of the summons has 3 variations to choose from and upgrade into. For Skeletal Warriors there is Skirmishers, Defenders, and Reapers. For the Skeletal Mages there is Shadow, Cold and Bone. For the Golem there is Blood, Bone, and Iron.  See below for more detail information on what we were able to see specifically for each of the variations.|Skeletal Warriors|-Skirmishers|-Defenders - Durable shield-bearers with 15% increased Life.|Upgrades |1. Every 10 seconds your Skeletal Defenders negate the next instance of Direct Damage they would take|2. Increase the amount of Thorns that Defender Warriors inherit from you from 30%-50%|3. Sacrifice - You gain 15% non-Physical Resistance, but you can no longer raise Skeletal Warriors|-Reapers|Skeletal Mages|-Shadow|-Cold - Chills and Freezes Enemies|Upgrades|1. Each time your Cold Mages damages enemies with their primary attack, you gain 2 essence|2. Enemies who are Frozen by or damage while Frozen by your Cold Mages' primary attack are made Vulnerable for 3 seconds|3. Sacrifice - You deal x15% increased damage to Vulnerable enemies, but you can no longer raise Skeletal Mages|-Bone - Uses its own bones as projectiles, dealing heavy damage for a Life cost.|Upgrades|1. Reduce the Life Cost of your Bone Mages attacks from 15% to 10%. After being alive for 5 seconds, Bone Mages deal 40% increased damage|2. Each time a Bone Mage dies from its own attack, they leave behind a corpse and Fortify you for 2,188|3. Sacrifice - Your Overpower damage is increased by 30%, but you can no longer raise Skeletal Mages|Golem |-Bone - Taunts enemies in a wide area.|Upgrades|1. Each time your Bone Golem takes up to 20% of its maximum life as damage, it sheds a Corpse.|2. Your Bone Golem gains 10% maximum life and the amount of Thorns they inherit from you is increased by 30% to 50%.|3. Sacrifice - you gain 10% increased Attack Speed, but you lose the ability to summon a Golem|-Blood - Drains Life from nearby enemies|Upgrades|1. Your Blood Golem absorbs 15% of damage you would take.|2. While Healthy, your Blood Golem gains 25% Damage Reduction and x25% increased damage|3. Sacrifice - Your maximum Life is increased by 10% but you lose the ability to summon a Golem|-Iron - Slams the ground and stuns enemies|Upgrades|1. Every 5th Iron Golem attack causes a shockwave dealing 16% damage to the primary enemy and enemies behind them|2. Your Iron Golem's slam attack also makes enemies Vulnerable for 3 seconds|3. Sacrifice - You deal x30% increased Critical Strike Damage, but you lose the ability to summon a Golem.|Hash Tags: #summergamefest, #diablo4, #d4|Timestamps:|0:05 Intro|0:15 Necromancer Single Golem Gameplay|1:25 Necromancer Skeletal Mages and Warriors Open Fields Gameplay|2:52 Necromancer Book of Dead Skills|3:11 Necromancer Iron Golem And Skeletons Dungeon Gameplay|6:25 PvP Gameplay|8:47 Open World Boss Gameplay

title: ZENVO COUNTDOWN! Completion News and Reveal Plans | ROAD TO ZENVO Part 8
description: There's not long to wait now! Let's get an update on the news of my Zenvo TSR-S and when all can be revealed, while experiencing some laps at Laguna Seca during Hypercar Invitational, in the very same car that visited @The Shmuseum, I cannot wait!|We've been following the Road to Zenvo story, and seen my car go from initial renders and specification through to updates from the build process in the assembly hall. However, as you can imagine it's nearly complete and talking with the Zenvo team, they have very kindly agreed to bring it over to the Goodwood Festival of Speed so that everyone can see it, ahead of my collection back from the factory in Denmark!|Zenvo are supporting the Hypercar Invitational weekend, involving a road drive, races on a runway, and now track time at the famous circuit of Laguna Seca. This means that they have brought out both the blue TSR-S that I drove on the roads local to my own garage, plus the white car that I've previously filmed before at @Topaz Detailing too.|That means for me, getting back behind the wheel of the same car on a new continent, to head out to the full Laguna Seca circuit for some fun laps. I must pre-empt that given the value of the car, and the importance of it being available for other events, plus my first laps ever at Laguna during a busy session, this is not about speed but about the feeling and excitement of getting out on track with this beast.|I cannot wait to see my car in a completed state, it's not going to be long now until it's ready to get out on the roads and be used as intended. If you are wondering why my car will return to Denmark after the Goodwood Festival of Speed, that's to both go through shakedown testing and also for my collection experience at the factory, so there's plenty more still to come in the Road to Zenvo.|Thanks for watching, Tim|Thank you to @rennphoto for the outro image! http://instagram.com/rennphoto|Chapters:|00:00 Intro|01:19 When is my Zenvo Ready?|04:36 Preparing for the Track|05:40 My First Drive at Laguna Seca|14:06 Thoughts from the Track|16:05 Hypercar Invitational|18:22 Wrap Up|#Zenvo #RoadtoZenvo #HypercarInvitational||||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

description: A Bhiwandi youth has been arrested for a social media post supporting suspended BJP neta Nupur Sharma. Police said that Saad Ansari, the accused, was arrested after a crowd reached outside his residence. They protested the social media post and demanded his arrest; police rushed to the spot. A case has been registered against him under section 153 A of Indian Penal Code (IPC). Bhiwandi police issued summons to Nupur Sharma on Saturday for her remarks against the Prophet. Watch the full video for more.|#nupursharma #bhiwandi #prophet #prophetmuhammad #prophetrow

title: Khilafatul Muslimin Punya "Menteri Pendidikan", Waspada Sebaran Doktrin Khilafah ke Sekolah-sekolah!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Polda Metro Jaya menangkap tokoh Khilafatul Muslimin yang berperan sebagai "Menteri Pendidikan" di kelompok itu.||||Kabid Humas Polda Metro Jaya, Kombes Endra Zulpan menyebut, orang yang ditangkap itu berperan memberikan doktrin Khilafah ke sekolah-sekolah.||||Sebelumnya, Zulpan juga menyampaikan bahwa Khilafatul Muslimin membuat nomor induk warga untuk menggantikan KTP elektronik yang diterbitkan pemerintah.||||Sementara, anggota Dewan Pengarah Badan Pembinaan Ideologi Pancasila (BPIP), Said Aqil Siroj meminta pemerintah menindak tegas organisasi Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Baca Juga Punya Jaringan di Seluruh Indonesia, Khilafatul Muslimin Dapat Pendanaan dari Ormas Asing! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298630/punya-jaringan-di-seluruh-indonesia-khilafatul-muslimin-dapat-pendanaan-dari-ormas-asing||||Dalam wawancara eksklusif dengan Jurnalis Kompas TV, Aiman Witjaksono, Pemimpin Khilaful Muslimin Jakarta Raya, Muhammad Abudan membantah memiliki Menteri Pertahanan, Menteri Ekonomi, Menteri Perhubungan, sampai Menteri Bidang Internasional.||||Menurut Direktur Pencegahan BNPT, Akhmad Nurwakhid, kelompok Khilafatul Muslimin biasa berbohong dan menghalalkan segala cara atas nama agama untuk mencapai tujuannya.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298679/khilafatul-muslimin-punya-menteri-pendidikan-waspada-sebaran-doktrin-khilafah-ke-sekolah-sekolah

title: WATCH: Why Bill Barr didnâ€™t believe Trumpâ€™s baseless election fraud claims | Jan. 6 hearings
description: In a recorded deposition played by the House committee investigating the Jan. 6 attack, Bill Barr addressed the myriad false claims of election fraud he encountered as the former attorney general.|â€œI was influenced by the fact that early claims that I understood were bogus and silly and usually based on misinformation, so I did not consider the quality of claims right out of the box to give me any feeling there was substance here,â€ he said in a video played on June 13.|Rep. Zoe Lofgren, D- Calif., noted that former President Donald Trump continued to lie about election fraud even after Barr told him those claims were false, adding that Trump berated and nearly fired Barr.|Barr said that he was particularly disturbed by baseless and â€œidioticâ€ claims regarding the functionality of Dominion Voting machines because they influenced members of the public, causing some to believe the nonsensical idea that the machines were controlled by people and emblematic of systemic corruption.|â€œI told them that it was crazy stuff and they were wasting their time on that,â€ Barr said. â€œIt was doing a great, grave disservice to the country.â€|Barr detailed an exchange with the former president in which Trump handed Barr a misleading report that he said indicated those machines were designed to engage in fraud. Barr emphasized that he did not see any information to support that conclusion.|â€œI was somewhat demoralized because I thought â€˜Boy, if he really believes this stuff, heâ€™s become detached from reality,â€™â€ Barr said. He added that when he told Trump that those allegations were â€œcrazy,â€ the former president did not show much interest in â€œwhat the actual facts were.â€ Barr reiterated that in his opinion, the 2020 presidential election was not stolen by fraud and he has not seen any evidence since then to change his mind.|The hearing was the second of several planned by the Jan. 6 committee that focused on how Trump actively spread false information about the 2020 election outcome â€“ what has become known as the â€œbig lieâ€ â€“ in the run up to the Jan. 6 insurrection. In the year since its creation, the committee has conducted more than 1,000 interviews, seeking critical information and documents from people witness to, or involved in, the violence that day.|Stream your PBS favorites with the PBS app: https://to.pbs.org/2Jb8twG|Find more from PBS NewsHour at https://www.pbs.org/newshour|Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://bit.ly/2HfsCD6|Follow us:|Facebook: http://www.pbs.org/newshour|Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/newshour|Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/newshour

title: Iko Uwais Diduga Lakukan Pemukulan, Polres Metro Bekasi Kota: Pelapor Adalah Tetangganya
description: KOMPAS.TV - Aktor laga Indonesia, Iko Uwais dilaporkan ke polisi atas kasus dugaan pemukulan dan pengeroyokan.||||Polisi menyebut, sebelum terjadi dugaan pemukulan, korban dan Iko Uwais sempat terlibat cekcok.||||Laporan soal dugaan pemukulan dan pengeroyokan yang dilakukan Iko Uwais dibenarkan Kabid Humas Polda Metro Jaya, Kombes Endra Zulpan.||||Saat ini, laporan sudah diterima Polres Metro Bekasi Kota.||||Polisi pun sudah memeriksa korban, melakukan visum, dan pemeriksaan saksi.||||Mapolres Metro Bekasi Kota juga membenarkan menerima laporan dugaan penganiayaan yang dilakukan aktor, Iko Uwais.||||Pelaporan dilakukan korban berinisial 'R', Sabtu malam (12/6).||||Selengkapnya terkait dugaan kasus pemukulan yang menyeret Iko Uwais, langsung Kompas TV tanyakan ke Kasat Reskrim Polres Metro Bekasi, Kompol Ivan Aditira.||||_____||||Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam nonstop di https://www.kompas.tv/live.||||Agar tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia.
